# geck0 Landing Page Rules

## Brand
- Name is always lowercase: **geck0** (never Geck0, GECK0, catrpillr)
- Logo: geck + purple "0" → `geck<span style="color:#7F77DD">0</span>`
- Tagline: "지식이 연결될 때, 회사가 진화합니다"
- Contact: hello@geck0.ai
- Domain: geck0.ai (app: app.geck0.ai)

## Colors
- Primary (purple): #7F77DD — logo, CTA, links
- Growth (teal): #1D9E75 — success states
- Energy (coral): #D85A30 — alerts, badges
- Background (navy): #1A1A2E

## Stack
- Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- framer-motion (installed) for animations
- i18n: ko/en via `src/lib/i18n/` — use `useI18n()` hook in client components

## Structure
- Main landing: `src/app/page.tsx`
- Pages: `/blog`, `/pricing`, `/enterprise`
- API: `/api/subscribe` for email CTA
- Blog posts: `src/content/blog/*.mdx`

## Conventions
- Add new copy to `src/lib/i18n/translations.ts` (both ko and en)
- Wrap sections with `<Reveal>` for scroll animations
- Use `<Logo />` component for brand mark
- Tone: intellectual but light, minimize jargon
